      For those of you flying in from out of town, thanks for making the trek and we hope you enjoy your time in Minnesota! Check out our <span class="content-link"><%= link_to "recommendations", recommendations_path %></span> for some things to do while you're in town if you have some time to explore.
    <br />
    <br />
