      Turn Left onto S Macalester St.  <br />
      In a couple of blocks, the parking lot will be on your left.  <br />
    <br />
    <br />
      For riders:  <br />
      We'll be providing transportation on good old fashioned yellow school buses from the hotel to the wedding and then back again. 
